						               													<description>Don't let anyone else lift the cup!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;FootClub is a card game with a tactical dimension in which you control everything: recruitment during the transfer window, team lineup, pre-match strategy and coaching during the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Footclub offers a total immersion into the football experience, including the thrill and emotions of a real football match!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;FootClub Ligue is a standalone extension of FootClub, which has the particularity of containing more components than the base box.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Stand alone: the box contains a complete set for 2 players, with 2 game modes available. Pee Wee mode (15 min): simple, accessible for all, perfect to discover the game, it will easily attract beginners as well as young players. Expert mode (60 min): strategically rich and with great replay value, it will satisfy experienced players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Extension: by combining with the FootClub box, discover the League mode for 4 players. This is how FootClub reveals its true dimension.&amp;#10;Manage your recruitment budget in a &amp;quot;tight&amp;quot; transfer window, based on auctions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Receive transfer offers. Will you withdraw a player despite a great offer?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Focus on your training centre: a young player can progress in a dazzling way to become a superstar!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Do you prefer short game sessions? It's simple and quick with the backup form.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Many new features and optional rules: new Match cards, new player positions, strengths of the goalkeepers, match on neutral ground.&amp;#10;Official rule of the Solo mode available for free download.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
